self_reporting: Fill out the questionnaire if you are ill and are getting tested, waiting on test results, received a positive COVID-19 test result, have had close contact with an individual who has a confirmed or suspected case of COVID-19, or if you have been asked to quarantine or isolate. Even if you are working with your local health department, please fill out the questionnaire, so USU officials may respond quickly to provide needed services or identify areas of our campuses that need additional attention.
